unpublishedAction.name: dndList

actionConfiguration.body:
() => {
		let dndCount = 0
		let reachable = 0
		getAllCustomersList.data.forEach(u => u.UsersDoNotDisturb == 0 ? dndCount+=1: reachable+=1)
		const ret = [{"x": "Reachable", "y": dndCount}, { "x": "Do not disturb", "y":reachable}]
		return ret
	}
